import React, { Component } from "react"; class CV extends Component { render() { const { data } = this.props; const skills = data.extraInfo.skills.keys(); const languages = data.extraInfo.languages.keys(); return (

{`${data.about.name} ${data.about.surname}`}

{data.about.email}

{data.about.address}

{data.about.phone}

{data.about.description}

{data.education[0].name}

{data.education[0].start}

{data.education[0].end}

{data.experience[0].name}

{data.experience[0].position}

{data.experience[0].start}

{data.experience[0].end}

{skills}

{languages}

); } } export default CV;
